eamforming. Such biases are shown to be corrected by using a local SoS map\nin beamforming, indicating the importance of and a need for local SoS\nreconstruction techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Jul 2021 17:06:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-21"}
