ng extended precision,\nchecking that the results are not affected by the level of precision,\ntruncation, etc.). Hence, we do not claim a computer-assisted proof, but the\nverification is more convincing that standard numerics. We hope that our work\ncould stimulate a computer-assisted proof.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Jul 2021 19:38:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-08"}
