g a significant improvement in comparison with state-of-the-art\nbackbone networks. The codes of this work will be available at\nhttps://github.com/danfenghong/IEEE_TGRS_SpectralFormer for the sake of\nreproducibility.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Jul 2021 02:59:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 20 Nov 2021 01:26:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-04"}
